snippet.title: Amnesia: Final Revelations trailer
snippet.description:
I know this isn't what I usually upload, but I wish to upload my mod on Steam and I need to upload a video from Youtube along side with the mod, so here it is ^^.  

Mod can be found here: http://www.moddb.com/mods/amnesia-final-revelations

(And on steam when it's up and running).
